com.knowledgebin.kb

Class SFSession

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.knowledgebin.kb.SFSession

  • public class SFSession
extends Object
    The SFSession is a composite object primarily containing means to provide a PartnerConnection object which is connected to SalesForce.com.

    If the server url and session id are known, then the partnerConnection object is created with these and returned.

    Otherwise if the username and password are specified, then these credentials are used to create a partnerConnection object and login to the SalesForce.com system.

    Otherwise if the OrgID is presented, then the SalesForce database is queried for the username and password for the specified OrgID and those credentials are used to create the partnerConnection object and login.
